Summary: Saw a Star-like object that flashed in 3 different colors in Glenview, Illinois.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside taking my dog out and looked out west towards the sky where I saw a strange star that was flickering red, green, and some other color which I cannot remember. I thought nothing of it and looked away for 2 minutes. I turn back to look back at it again, but it was gone...I saw somebody else from Illinois who posted the same thing I exactly saw and Im telling you man you are not alone.
